Date><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国进口恢复增长但出口放缓引发前景担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</link><description>7月份，中国的出口增长速度为三个月来最慢，低于预期，加剧了人们对庞大制造业前景的担忧，而在美国预期的科技限制措施之前急于增加芯片供应，导致进口增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:52:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国、澳大利亚、加拿大将在南海举行首次联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>菲律宾、加拿大、美国和澳大利亚四国军方表示，周三在南海举行了首次联合军事演习，以加强两国军队之间的互操作性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大清算人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，陷入困境的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的清算人已对普华永道采取法律行动，指责其在为集团工作时“疏忽”和“失实陈述”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行暗示在市场波动期间不会加息，日元暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-yen-wobbles-traders-consider-rate-cut-bets-carry-2024-08-07/</link><description>日元周三暴跌，此前一位有影响力的日本央行官员淡化了近期加息的可能性，本周出现新的转折，美国经济衰退担忧和热门套利交易平仓推动了大规模走势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-yen-wobbles-traders-consider-rate-cut-bets-carry-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行放弃加息后亚洲股市上涨，日元回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-07/</link><description>亚洲股市周三延续涨势，日经指数再次反弹，日本央行在市场波动中意外对加息持谨慎态度，导致日元大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>Shabab Al-Ahli 在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中发起了 Al-Gharafa 冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</link><description>阿拉伯联合酋长国的沙巴布·阿赫利在伊斯法罕加时赛中以 4-1 的比分战胜伊朗东道主塞帕汉，下周将迎战卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法，争夺新一届亚洲冠军联赛精英赛的小组赛席位。周二。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 00:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>面对中国的“胁迫”，美国将增加澳大利亚的兵力投送</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</link><description>两国在年度防务会谈后表示，澳大利亚将于明年开始与美国共同制造制导武器，以增加对印太地区盟国的供应，并增加美国在该国的军事存在，包括轰炸机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:14:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：“周二周转”暂时缓解紧张情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-06/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求改善，Vans 母公司 VF Corp 第一季度营收降幅小于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>VF Corp 周二公布，由于中国业务改善以及库存水平下降，第一季度营收降幅小于预期，导致其股价在盘后交易中上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国学者在美充当外国代理人被判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，一名中国学者被判在美国非法充当外国代理人，他收集了纽约支持中国民主的活动人士的信息，并与北京分享了他的调查结果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社称，巴基斯坦已获得主要贷方一年期债务展期的承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-has-one-year-debt-rollover-commitments-key-lenders-bloomberg-says-2024-08-06/</link><description>据彭博社周二报道，巴基斯坦已获得中国、沙特阿拉伯和阿联酋的承诺，将债务展期一年，这对等待国际货币基金组织最终批准一项新的 70 亿美元贷款计划的卡拉奇来说是一个提振。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-has-one-year-debt-rollover-commitments-key-lenders-bloomberg-says-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>